OL,3,CSmartphones: Time To Live Without Them?
OL,5,FFifty years after the first handheld
OL,6,Fcell phone call was made, the digital
OL,7,Flandscape has changed beyond
OL,8,Frecognition. Mobile telephones are now
OL,9,Fan essential modern day multi-tool,
OL,10,Fwith new research showing 14% of teens
OL,11,Fexhibit addictive-like behaviours to
OL,12,Fsocial media.
OL,14,FIn this episode of ITV's Tonight
OL,15,Fprogramme, Faye Barker finds out more
OL,16,Fabout smartphones and whether it's
OL,17,Ftime we give them up.
