OL,3,CSmartphones: Time To Live Without Them?
OL,5,FTwelve months ago the then
OL,6,FConservative government passed the
OL,7,FOnline Safety Act with the goal of
OL,8,Fkeeping dangerous content away from
OL,9,Fvulnerable eyes. Whilst the current
OL,10,Fage limit on social media sites
OL,11,FSnapchat, Instagram, TikTok and
OL,12,FFacebook is 13, research by media
OL,13,Fregulator OFCOM shows that 91% of 12-
OL,14,F15 year olds own a smartphone. Their
OL,15,Fdata extends to show children as young
OL,16,Fas 9-years-old are being exposed to
OL,17,Fpornography.
