OL,3,CSmartphones: Time To Live Without Them?
OL,5,FWith growing concern among parents
OL,6,Fabout the powers of 'big tech', the
OL,7,FTonight programme speaks to Daisy
OL,8,FGreenwell and Joe Ryrie from
OL,9,FSmartphone Free Childhood who are
OL,10,Fleaders in a growing movement of
OL,11,Fparents pledging to delay giving their
OL,12,Fchildren smartphones for as long as
OL,13,Fpossible. Daisy started the Whatsapp
OL,14,Fgroup with her friend Clare back in
OL,15,FFebruary, and after her social media
OL,16,Fpost went viral online, within 24hrs
OL,17,Fthousands of other worried parents had
OL,18,Fjoined the group.
